'''''The Hatred Vector''''' was a planned four-part comic miniseries that would have been set prior to ''[[The New Jedi Order: Vector Prime]]'' and would have detailed the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] preparing for their [[Yuuzhan Vong War|invasion]] of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. It would possibly have been a direct lead-in to ''Vector Prime''.

